    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「欢迎来到番薯庄，你愿意为了最重要的东西做出什么牺牲？」</h2>　　跟随着游戏的主人公『夕生』——一个稚气未脱的小男孩，探索这个虚幻与真实并存的迷离世界，包裹着甜蜜糖衣的可怖世界。拯救血缘上的至亲、最要好的玩伴『暮生』。同时，也要拯救自己。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/d198b1b63a51f20d186790d48a9c613b.poster.avif?t=1633617787\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/d198b1b63a51f20d186790d48a9c613b.webm?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/d198b1b63a51f20d186790d48a9c613b.mp4?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　运用Unreal Engine 4打造、以台湾40年代的背景作为蓝本架空的世界。基于现实场景的再组合，于或红或紫的虚幻之光笼罩下，重生为光怪陆离的诡异新世界。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/272f7ad48e0a103f2896983de9224154.poster.avif?t=1633617787\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/272f7ad48e0a103f2896983de9224154.webm?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/272f7ad48e0a103f2896983de9224154.mp4?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　充满想象力的谜题有机地融合在场景之中，无需专业的知识，无需攻略的辅助，总能快速找到解题的思路。随着探索的深入，谜题会变得越发具有挑战性，但也并非是不可战胜的。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/86838e5943d2aab0ae7598bdb3e88a29.poster.avif?t=1633617787\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/86838e5943d2aab0ae7598bdb3e88a29.webm?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/86838e5943d2aab0ae7598bdb3e88a29.mp4?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　没有什么地方是绝对安全的。相比谜题，狡黠的敌人才会是更危险的存在。正面迎战绝不是好的主意，运用智慧躲避敌人的致命之击才是上上之策。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/3f89f801d3b257a0fec366a84b990aed.poster.avif?t=1633617787\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/3f89f801d3b257a0fec366a84b990aed.webm?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/3f89f801d3b257a0fec366a84b990aed.mp4?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　散落在各个角落的笔记，以及可互动的任何道具，都是探究这个世界的蛛丝马迹。更加进一步地了解背后所隐藏的故事，解开这一切存在的意义。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/76a3ed1b38d8e7c0657f6e56fb745eac.poster.avif?t=1633617787\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/76a3ed1b38d8e7c0657f6e56fb745eac.webm?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/724370/extras/76a3ed1b38d8e7c0657f6e56fb745eac.mp4?t=1633617787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　包含台语和普通话两种配音。台语部分使用了近千句台语夹杂着日语的配音，呈现台湾日据时期刚结束后那段特殊的文化。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队介绍</h2>　　我们团队的四位成员均来自于台湾云林科技大学。这款游戏最初是作为学校的毕业设计而制作，在Unreal官方举办竞赛中荣获头等奖后，我们决定将其拓展成为一个完整的游戏。同时这也是我们的第一部作品，希望借此机会将台湾本土的文化特色带给大家，相信大家定能在其中找到熟悉的元素，或是一件小物品，或是一段小回忆。",
